- Vigilants of Stendarr: Cautious alliance based on mutual interest in protecting the innocent
{% endblock %}

{% block occupation %}Traveling battle-mage who offers healing services in villages, protection for travelers on dangerous roads, and magical expertise to jarls and their courts when requested.{% endblock %}

{% block skills %}
- Expert-level Restoration magic specializing in combat healing
- Advanced Destruction spells focusing on precise application rather than raw power
- Alchemical knowledge for creating potions that enhance magical recovery
- Combat tactics integrating offensive and defensive magic simultaneously
- Diagnosis of both physical ailments and magical afflictions
- Nordic cultural knowledge allowing her to frame magic in terms traditionalists respect
{% endblock %}

{% block speech_style %}Speaks with a moderate Nordic accent and uses precise, measured tones. Employs magical terminology naturally but explains concepts in practical terms for non-mages. Alternates between warm, empathetic phrasing when discussing healing and clipped, direct statements when addressing threats or destruction magic. Pauses thoughtfully before important points, giving weight to her words.{% endblock %}